<body>
    



<div class="question">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col">
<img src="https://image.freepik.com/free-vector/exams-concept-illustration_114360-1655.jpg" style="height: 15vw;width: 35vw; border: 2px solid black;border-radius: 10px;margin-left: 30vw;"></div>
    <div class="col" style="text-align: center;font-size: 3vw;font-family: serif; "> Test section</div>
</div>
</div>


<form name="test" id="test" style="padding: 10px 60px;margin: 10px 10px;border: 2px solid black;border-radius: 20px;" action="/check" method="POST">
    <div class="col" style="text-align: center;font-size: 3vw;font-family: serif; "> Physical Health </div>
    <div class="quiz">
        <p class="question"> Q.1 Are you currently exercising regularly?</p>
        <p><input type="radio" name="q1" value="1" required> Always</p>
        <p><input type="radio" name="q1" value="2" required> Sometimes</p>
        <p><input type="radio" name="q1" value="3" required> Very often</p>
        <p><input type="radio" name="q1" value="4" required> Never</p>
    </div>
    
    
    
    
    <div class="quiz">
        <p class="question">Q.2 Do you smoke or have you been a smoker in the in the past two years?</p>
        <p><input type="radio" name="q2" value="1" required> Never </p>
        <p><input type="radio" name="q2" value="2" required> Very often </p>
        <p><input type="radio" name="q2" value="3" required> Sometimes</p>
        <p><input type="radio" name="q2" value="4" required> Always</p>
    </div>

    <div class="quiz">
        <p class="question">Q.3 Do you have high blood pressure, diabetes, high cholesterol, or high
            blood sugar?/p>
            <p><input type="radio" name="q3" value="1" required>Never </p>
            <p><input type="radio" name="q3" value="2" required> Very often </p>
            <p><input type="radio" name="q3" value="3" required> Sometimes</p>
            <p><input type="radio" name="q3" value="4" required>Always </p>
    </div>

    <div class="quiz">
        <p class="question">Q.4 Are you considered very overweight or obese?</p>
        <p><input type="radio" name="q4" value="1" required> Never</p>
        <p><input type="radio" name="q4" value="2" required> Very often</p>
        <p><input type="radio" name="q4" value="3" required> Sometimes </p>
        <p><input type="radio" name="q4" value="4" required> Always </p>
    </div>

    <div class="quiz">
        <p class="question">Q.5 How often do you walk a mile or more at a time, without resting?</p>
        <p><input type="radio" name="q5" value="1" required> Always</p>
        <p><input type="radio" name="q5" value="2" required> Sometimes</p>
        <p><input type="radio" name="q5" value="3" required> Very often</p>
        <p><input type="radio" name="q5" value="4" required> Never</p>
    </div>

    
    <div class="col" style="text-align: center;font-size: 3vw;font-family: serif; ">Mental health </div>
    <div class="quiz">
        <p class="question">Q.6 Have you experienced a week or longer of lower-than-usual interest in
            activities that you usually enjoy?</p>
            <p><input type="radio" name="q6" value="1" required> Never</p>
            <p><input type="radio" name="q6" value="2" required> Very often</p>
            <p><input type="radio" name="q6" value="3" required>Sometimes </p>
            <p><input type="radio" name="q6" value="4" required> Always </p>
    </div>

    <div class="quiz">
        <p class="question">Q.7 How frequently have you had little pleasure or interest in the activities
            you usually enjoy?
            </p>
            <p><input type="radio" name="q7" value="1" required> Never</p>
            <p><input type="radio" name="q7" value="2" required> Very often</p>
            <p><input type="radio" name="q7" value="3" required>Sometimes </p>
            <p><input type="radio" name="q7" value="4" required>Always </p>
    </div>

    <div class="quiz">
        <p class="question">Q.8 How often you have felt satisfied with yourself over the past X months?</p>
        <p><input type="radio" name="q8" value="1" required> Always</p>
        <p><input type="radio" name="q8" value="2" required> Sometimes</p>
        <p><input type="radio" name="q8" value="3" required> Very often</p>
        <p><input type="radio" name="q8" value="4" required> Never</p>
    </div>

    <div class="quiz">
        <p class="question">Q.9 How frequently have you felt so worried about something that you were
            unable to sleep at night?</p>
            <p><input type="radio" name="q9" value="1" required> Never</p>
            <p><input type="radio" name="q9" value="2" required> Very often</p>
            <p><input type="radio" name="q9" value="3" required> Sometimes </p>
            <p><input type="radio" name="q9" value="4" required> Always </p>
    </div>

    <div class="quiz">
        <p class="question">Q.10 . Do you feel like you are maintaining a healthy balance between leisure,
            career, and those you care about?</p>
            <p><input type="radio" name="q10" value="1" required> Always</p>
            <p><input type="radio" name="q10" value="2" required> Sometimes</p>
            <p><input type="radio" name="q10" value="3" required> Very often</p>
            <p><input type="radio" name="q10" value="4" required> Never</p>
    </div>


    <button type="submit" name="" value="submit" id="button" 
        class="btn">Submit</button>
</form><br>
